MERGE (ak_ALTERNATIVE_TO:Meta:ArcKind {key: 'ALTERNATIVE_TO'})
ON CREATE SET
  ak_ALTERNATIVE_TO.display_name = 'Alternative To',
  ak_ALTERNATIVE_TO.llm_context = 'Alternative relationship: Entity A is an alternative to Entity B (symmetric). Entities can substitute for each other in certain contexts. alternative_type: equivalent (same purpose), similar (close match), fallback (backup option), upgrade (better), downgrade (simpler) Examples: VCard ALTERNATIVE_TO MeCard, PNG ALTERNATIVE_TO JPG Symmetric: A ALTERNATIVE_TO B implies B ALTERNATIVE_TO A. Differs from COMPETES_WITH: alternatives can coexist, competitors fight.',
